ctrlShow 
Behavior: local 
Game: Operation Flashpoint (1.5) 
Description: Set if a control of the currently active user dialog is shown or not. 
Read Dialog Control for more information about user dialogs and controls 
.  
Syntax:  
 ctrlShow [idc, show] 
Parameters: 
[idc, show]: Array 
idc: Integer - control ID 
show: Boolean - true if the control should be shown, false if not 
Return Value: 
 Nothing